\f1\b\fs52 \cb3 Closing Thoughts\'a0\cb1 \

\f0\b0\fs36 \cb3 Man may not be as rational as the economists might think.\cb1 \
\cb3 Although we are biased, I suppose that it is just part of being human and that it\'92s alright to be biased. We can\'92t run away from our biases, but at least we can learn to identify them and find ways to cope with them.\'a0\cb1 \
